#######################################
##############EXERCISE 07##############
#######################################

The folder contains three subfolders related to the
three points of the exercise.
The code and the results of Exercise 07.3 are in the
folder related to the Optional Exercise of the Molecular
Dynamics.
In each of this folder is present a makefile: if deemed 
appropriate code the 'make' command to generate the executable
'Monte_Carlo_NVT.exe'; otherwise, folders already contain simulation 
results saved to files typically in .dat format.
The comment on the results is contained in the 
jupyter-notebook named 'Numerical Exercises 7.ipynb'
